title: #213 - Danny Gonzalez
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined by YouTuber, comedian, former Vine star and all around wholesome dude Danny Gonzalez! Together we discuss his feet, TikTok getting shut down, throwing other creators under the bus, and together we assemble the ultimate influencer in the wild tier list!
